  "subject": "[COMMON] Enforce pylint tox profile & score>=5.35",
  "commit_message": "[COMMON] Enforce pylint tox profile & score>=5.35\n\n- generate a pylint configuration file with pylint --generate-rcfile\n  to avoid passing many arguments to pylint command in tox profile\n- split the current profile in 2 with:\n  * a \"pylint\" profile with minimal output (-E option)\n  * a \"pylint_full\" profile more verbose and with reports\n- enforce the pylint tox profile in tox.ini envlist\n\nIssue-ID: OOM-2643\nSigned-off-by: guillaume.lambert <guillaume.lambert@orange.com>\nChange-Id: I83cf5945ff511cdb9fd0e53fa6f2753dac47ea9f\n",
